Class Atan

java.lang.Object
org.moeaframework.util.tree.Node
org.moeaframework.util.tree.Atan
public class Atan extends Node
The node for calculating the arc tangent of a number. The inputs and outputs to this node are shown below:
Name Type Description
Argument 1 Number The number
Return Value Number The arc tangent of the number
